OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,FAndy Burnham has vowed to "change
OL,8,FLabour" and improve the lives of
OL,9,Fvoters in Makerfield if elected.
OL,11,FSpeaking at the Great North Investment
OL,12,FSummit, The Mayor of Greater
OL,13,FManchester set out his vision for how
OL,14,Fthe country should be run to ensure a
OL,15,F"fairer" society for everyone.
OL,17,FAndy Burnham recently announced his
OL,18,Fintention to return to Westminster
OL,19,Fafter the resignation of Josh Simons
OL,20,Fas the MP for Makerfield.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
