FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,FMr Simons announced his resignation on
OL,8,FThursday 14 May so Mr Burnham can
OL,9,F"drive the change our country is
OL,10,Fcrying out for".
OL,12,FDuring his speech, Andy Burnham said
OL,13,Fthat voters in the North of England
OL,14,F"deserve a bigger response than
OL,15,Fpoliticians have given them before"
OL,16,Fand vowed to do more for the public if
OL,17,Felected as an MP.
OL,26,@qD@AOUrD@OO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39503
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,FHe said the Makerfield contest would
OL,8,Fbe "no ordinary by-election" and hit
OL,9,Fout at the current Labour Government
OL,10,Fwith a promise he will change the
OL,11,Fparty if elected.
OL,13,FHe said: "In my view, the time has
OL,14,Fcome for a much bigger debate about
OL,15,Fhow politics needs to change if it is
OL,16,Fto work properly for the North of
OL,17,FEngland, because it doesn't.
OL,19,F"This is what we've got to focus on.
OL,20,FPeople are losing faith in politics."
OL,26,@pD@DOUpD@\O]uD@JOU|D@eO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39504
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,FLaying out his "ambitious" plan for
OL,8,FMakerfield if elected, Mr Burnham said
OL,9,Fhe would lift up its people and make
OL,10,Flife easier.
OL,12,FHe said: "It will involve action to
OL,13,Fmake the basics of life more
OL,14,Faffordable, like rents, bills, and
OL,15,Ffares.
OL,17,F"All rail stations and services in
OL,18,FMakerfield coming into the Bee network
OL,19,Fand leading to a big reduction for
OL,20,Fpeople in the cost of public transport
OL,21,Fand cost of travel."
OL,26,@tD@JOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39505
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,FHe went on to say that Britain has
OL,8,Fbeen on a "wrong path for 40 years"
OL,9,Fthat has damaged communities in the
OL,10,FNorth of England.
OL,12,FHe said: "The deindustrialization of
OL,13,Fthe 1980s was devastating for places
OL,14,Facross Makerfield like Ashton-in-
OL,15,FMakerfield, Orrel, Winstanley,
OL,16,FHindley, Platbridge.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39506
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,F"Privatisation in the 90s and
OL,8,Fausterity in the 2010s... It all adds
OL,9,Fup to 40 years of neoliberalism that
OL,10,Fhave not been kind to the north of
OL,11,FEngland."
OL,13,FThe Mayor of Greater Manchester said
OL,14,Fthe current systems in place are not
OL,15,Fdesigned to help normal people with
OL,16,Fday-to-day issues like fixing potholes
OL,17,For improving communities.
OL,19,FHe also hit out at what he called a
OL,20,F"failure of national government to
OL,21,Fprotect local government".
OL,26,@}D@YO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,FThe Greater Manchester Mayor said: "If
OL,8,Fpolitics can't fix something as simple
OL,9,Fas a pothole, you've got a very big
OL,10,Fproblem.
OL,12,F"Why should people have faith in the
OL,13,Fability of politics to do anything if
OL,14,Fit can't do something as simple as
OL,15,Fthat?"
OL,17,FMr Burnham suggested bringing a number
OL,18,Fof services into public control would
OL,19,Fgive local authorities more power to
OL,20,Fensure communities are being best
OL,21,Fserved.
OL,26,@oD@dOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39508
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,FHe said: "We have an unaccountable
OL,8,Fstate where too much is delivered by
OL,9,Farm's length or outsourced agencies
OL,10,Fthat local councils can't control.
OL,12,F"So many crucial services like housing
OL,13,Fand energy delivered by fragmented
OL,14,Fagencies outside of local democratic
OL,15,Fcontrol."
OL,17,FThe Mayor pledged to "transfer power
OL,18,Fand resources back to local areas" if
OL,19,Felected and criticised the "halfway
OL,20,Fhouse" approach taken by the current
OL,21,FGovernment.
OL,26,@yD@VOUzD@bO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39509
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,FHe said: "Something gets devolved, but
OL,8,Fnone of the people get devolved, and
OL,9,Fthey sit there marking the homework of
OL,10,Fthe combined authorities and finding
OL,11,Fnew ways of putting pressure on to do
OL,12,Fsomething that they want.
OL,14,F"It's time to trust the region's
OL,15,Foffice of this country, free them up,
OL,16,Flet them get on with the job."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39510
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,FMr Burnham also used his speech to
OL,8,Finsist he did not want to reignite the
OL,9,Fdebate on whether to rejoin the
OL,10,FEuropean Union, despite saying during
OL,11,Fthe Labour Party's 2025 Conference he
OL,12,Fwould like to see Brexit reversed in
OL,13,Fhis life time.
OL,15,FHe said: "My view is that Brexit has
OL,16,Fbeen damaging, but I also believe the
OL,17,Flast thing we should do right now is
OL,18,Fre-run those arguments. Britain will
OL,19,Fbe stuck in a permanent rut if we're
OL,20,Fjust constantly arguing and people are
OL,21,Fpulling away from each other.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,F"It is time, surely, isn't it, to
OL,8,Fbring people back together, to focus
OL,9,Fon what we've got in common, to get
OL,10,Fthe growth coming to all places, so
OL,11,Fit's felt there.
OL,13,F"That is what we need in this moment
OL,14,Fand it's really important that
OL,15,Fwhatever comes out of this by-election
OL,16,Fthere is a more unifying feeling about
OL,17,Fthe change that we need to work
OL,18,Ftowards.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39512
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,F"I am not proposing that the UK
OL,8,Fconsiders rejoining the EU. I respect
OL,9,Fthe decision that was made at the
OL,10,Freferendum and it is going to
OL,11,Fundermine everything I have said about
OL,12,Fstrengthening democracy if we don't
OL,13,Frespect that vote."
OL,15,FAndy Burnham ended his speech with an
OL,16,Fadmition that what had been offered in
OL,17,Fthe past by Labour "has simply not
OL,18,Fbeen good enough" and vowed to change
OL,19,Fthe party if elected.
OL,26,@oD@AOUuD@SO]yD@TOUzD@QO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39513
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,FHe said "I'm clear about what I am
OL,8,Foffering. If I get to stand, a vote
OL,9,Ffor me will be a vote to change
OL,10,FLabour, because Labour needs to change
OL,11,Fif we are to regain people's trust.
OL,13,F"It will be a vote to make life more
OL,14,Faffordable again, a vote to power up
OL,15,Fplaces, a vote to reindustrialise.
OL,26,@oD@IOUuD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,396,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39514
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1779174391
OL,3,CAndy Burnham sets out vision to
OL,4,C'change Labour' and give power back to
OL,5,Cthe North
OL,7,F"This is the choice in this by-
OL,8,Felection. Do you want Makerfield and
OL,9,Fthe North to stay on the same path
OL,10,Fit's been for the last 40 years, or do
OL,11,Fyou want a new path which brings the
OL,12,Fcountry back together and makes it
OL,13,Fwork for everyone?
OL,15,F"I know why I'm standing, I know what
OL,16,FI'm offering.
OL,18,F"I know what my party has offered in
OL,19,Fthe past has simply not been good
OL,20,Fenough."
OL,26,@oD@AOUwD@AOUzD@AOU|D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
